<li class="menu__item is-expanded expanded menu__link"><a href="/virgin-red" class="menu__link">Virgin Red</a><ul class="menu"><li class="menu__item is-leaf first leaf menu__link mobile-only"><a href="/virgin-red" class="menu__link mobile-only">Virgin Red</a></li>
